{"word":"ἀπροσδόκητος","slug":"ἀπροσδόκητος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπροσδόκητος</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unexpected, unlooked for</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐξ ἀπροσδοκήτου</el>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>necopinato</el>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; so <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-τως</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>not expecting, unaware</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}